                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            <h2>IPU B.Tech Admission via JEE Main – Overview</h2>
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    <p>Guru Gobind Singh Indraprastha University (GGSIPU) offers B.Tech admission primarily based on <strong>JEE Main scores</strong>. JEE Main is the first-preference entrance exam for all B.Tech seats at IP University affiliated engineering colleges in Delhi NCR.</p>
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            <h2 style="margin-top:35px;">Eligibility for IPU B.Tech via JEE Main</h2>
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    <ul>
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  <li>Minimum 55% marks in Class 12 with Physics, Chemistry and Mathematics (PCM)</li>
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            <li>Must have qualified JEE Main (Paper 1) in the relevant year</li>
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      <li>JEE Main score is the primary admission criteria</li>
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                <li>Participation in centralized GGSIPU counselling is mandatory</li>
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        </ul>
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                <h2 style="margin-top:35px;">Step-by-Step: IPU B.Tech JEE Main Admission Process</h2>
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        <ol>
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      <li><strong>Appear in JEE Main</strong> – Register and qualify JEE Main (conducted by NTA)</li>
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                <li><strong>GGSIPU Registration</strong> – Register on the official IPU admission portal</li>
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          <li><strong>Document Upload</strong> – Upload Class 12 marksheet, JEE scorecard, photo and ID</li>
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    <li><strong>Choice Filling & Locking</strong> – Fill college and branch preferences in order of priority</li>
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              <li><strong>Seat Allotment</strong> – Multiple rounds of seat allotment based on JEE rank</li>
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        <li><strong>Document Verification</strong> – Report for document verification at allotted college</li>
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  <li><strong>Fee Payment & Reporting</strong> – Pay admission fee and confirm seat</li>
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          </ol>
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          
