                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            <h2 style="margin-top:35px;">JEE Main vs CUET for IPU B.Tech</h2>
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    <p>JEE Main is given <strong>first preference</strong> for all B.Tech seats at IPU. CUET may serve as a secondary pathway. Students with strong JEE Main scores should prioritize GGSIPU counselling via JEE rank. For CUET pathway, see <a href="ipu-btech-via-cuet.php">IPU B.Tech via CUET guide</a>.</p>
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            <h2 style="margin-top:35px;">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    <h3>Q: What JEE Main rank do I need for MAIT or MSIT?</h3>
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            <p>Cutoffs vary each year. Generally, top colleges like MAIT, MSIT require JEE Main ranks in the lower range for popular branches like CSE. Contact our helpline for updated cutoff guidance.</p>
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    <h3 style="margin-top:20px;">Q: Can I get management quota B.Tech without high JEE rank?</h3>
